            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;In case of using an authentication, &lt;code&gt;Access-Control-Allow-Origin&lt;/code&gt; does not accept the &lt;code&gt;*&lt;/code&gt; in some browsers (FF and Chrome AFAIK). So in this case you have to specify the value from the &lt;code&gt;Origin&lt;/code&gt; header. Hope that this will help someone.&lt;/span&gt;

